Text: Request for Electronic copy of NDATana I have been asked if we could please be provided an electronic version of the NonDisclosure Agreement that you and I worked on together on Monday between Cap Gemini Ernst Young U S LLC Enron Net Works LLC and EnronOnline LLC By the way I just received the interoffice envelope with the two originals and I will have Eric Grest sign them both I will return one fully executed original to you ASAP thank you very much Would it be possible to receive the electronic version today as Im scheduling a conference call for the CGEY people and they must each have a copy of the agreement prior to the call Thank you very much Marianne Ext
